data.description: Found in the well-positioned and convenient neighborhood of Champions Park located on the outskirts of 1604. Its proximity to major routes like 90 makes commuting to various destinations, such as Lackland Air Force Base, the tech companies within TRP, the Medical district, or downtown, a convenient and straightforward driving experience.  The home itself offers 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, a spacious and open floor plan, providing a comfortable setting for entertaining guests or spending time with family.   Located in the highly rated Medina Valley Independent School District is a notable advantage, ensuring access to quality education for families residing in the area.   Offering  a blend of convenience, comfort, and educational opportunities, this home is an attractive option for those looking for a residence in San Antonio!
